_sText:
After making a few surf maps i figured it was time to make a regular map :)

CT/Ts both start out on opposite sides of the map.
you can either head for bombsite B at the buildings or head for one of the corners and take the tunnels to bombsite A.
you can also goto the middle and scale a ladder then head down to bombsite A, but its a good place to get shot.

cause surfin is fun includes skybox surfing if you can get there
theres also fun with gman and pigeons in the area of bombsite A (shoot some walls)
